Morecambe say they are dealing with the matter internally.

A spokesman for Preston North End said: 'At the time of the incident, Sam Livesey was playing for Morecambe and we therefore have no comment to make.'

Tuohy spent four hours at hospital after the game after complaining of concussion-like symptoms.

After the game he tweeted: 'Good 7-2 win good to get a goal and head is killing me now wow.'

 

